item.title: Leetspeak
item.description: is an app that can be used to translate letters into similar looking numbers. It doesn’t matter whether a letter, a word or more is entered There are three ways to use the Leetspeak Generator: simple leet (predefined) extended leet (predefined) custom leet (create your own leet)
